Description: Fine-loamy, mixed Ultic Hapludalfs. Soils in Morrison serie are sandy loam, very deep with 2 to 8 percent slopes, well-drained, formed in residuum of weathered  noncalcareous sandstone. The permeability is moderate to moderately rapid.
